{
  "stem": "20848.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anyway, they put this-- they burned this house, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And now, my uncle and his wife and my little cousin got-- we got together and we started running.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we ran to a house in a different street where it was empty.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, there were no Jewish people there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was completely empty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they had a commander that came and cleared up completely these flats.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Not for cleanliness sake, but they robbed it, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They took every piece of furniture, everything, and they sent it to Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they had a commander called [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What they did was they took the [NON-ENGLISH] covers, and sent it to Germany and left the feathers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And anyway, there was my-- the four of us and my uncle and my little cousin and auntie.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And two ladies attached themselves to us, and a man.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't-- I don't know how many, I never counted how many we were.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But we got-- we must have met the other people in that flat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We got to the flat and it was empty.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there was nothing there except the feathers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we were sitting there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "By that time, we didn't eat anything for three days because we didn't have any food at all, none of us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, we hear this German marching from flat to flat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So we hid underneath the feathers, all of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the Germans came to the apartment and they didn't see us and they went away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And my mother said, oh, aren't we lucky they didn't get us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But half an hour later, they came again and it was really lucky that they did find us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "One of the ladies foot was protruding from the feathers.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
